U.S.-Swiss Tax Deal May Fail in Parliament, NZZ am Sonntag Says

-- B y   T h o m a s   M u l i e r
-- 
2011-09-18T07:52:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-18/u-s-swiss-tax-deal-may-fail-in-parliament-nzz-am-sonntag-says.html
A U.S.-Swiss agreement on a tax
dispute over offshore bank accounts may fail this week in
 Switzerland ’s parliament,  NZZ am Sonntag  said.  The Swiss People’s Party and the  Liberal Party  have decided
to reject an amended version that would allow the U.S. to submit
inquiries about bank accounts of U.S. citizens in groups, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Mulier in Geneva at 
 tmulier@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net  